<p>Here I&#8217;ll aim to put some silly stats I&#8217;ve picked up from people and newspapers. I&#8217;ll try and verify them, as some of them are hard to believe.</p>

<ul>
<li>Kissing was banned on TV until only 10 years ago</li>
<li>Seoul has the largest metro system <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Subways">verified</a> &#8211; though much of it is above ground (cheating!)</li>
<li>Highest (alcohol) drinking for a developed nation</li>
<li>Highest road accidents for a developed nation</li>
<li>Highest broadband penetration <a href="http://adslguide.org.uk/newsarchive.asp?item=2630">2nd to Iceland</a></li>
