<p>&#8220;Developed nation&#8221; statistics are usually compiled by the <a href="http://www.oecd.org/">Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development</a> and their member countries. Unfortunately their website is terrible as most of the stats are in PDFs and hence completely useless.</p>